Nora: But...I always remembered who I was.

Nora: In the memory I accessed, the real Nora...

Nora: Therefore, I understand you not being able to let go of Kittyeyes and the others. Nevertheless, even if it's painful sometimes,
Nora: for the happiness of our loved ones, "we" still need to hold firm to our decisions...
